NXT Stand and Deliver 04-06-2024

Philadelphia, PA

Pre Show

1.  **_Joe Gacy vs Shawn Spears_**
    
    Ridge Holland returns after his false retirement to take out Joe Gacy. Gacy fights back and pulls it out.
    
    **_WINNER: Joe Gacy_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b4bc37dd-cb59-40a3-b58b-c2e86c551b64/Screenshot_20240406-092344_X.jpg)

*   ## **_NXT TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: WOLFDOGS VS AXIOM AND NATHAN FRAISER_**
    

Incredible opening tag match from all parties. Go out of your way to see it.

*   **_WINNER: WOLFDOGS_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5cb487dc-10e5-46dc-ac2a-3b7e4d5f93a2/20240406_093412.jpg)

Meta Four introduce us to Oba Femi before some heavy Paramount/Knuckles advertising

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/df751d68-a76e-426a-a37f-6c52bb09304f/20240406_095317.jpg)

*   **_NXT NORTH AMERICAN CHAMPIONSHIP OBA FEMI VS DIJAK VS JOSH RIGGS_**
    

Incredible HOSS action from all three. Just the RIGHT amount of wreckless and scary.

*   **_WINNER: OBA FEMI RETAINS_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9f85c69b-f1e8-48b5-9e63-b21ddf470fa4/20240406_095321.jpg)

