*   **_Six Woman Tag Team Match: Thea Hail, Kelani Jordan and Fallon Henley vs Izzy Dame, Jacy Jayne and Kiana James._**
    

These girls worked so much harder than I ever expected. Great work.

*   **_WINNER: Thea Hail, Kelani Jordan and Fallon Henley_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0f2ef578-3ef4-4d64-8002-3261bfdf499c/20240406_101715.jpg)

NXT announced a mid card championship for the women!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1328175d-b13b-4af9-974f-fe5056463428/20240406_102134.jpg)

GIULIA HAS ARRIVED IN NXT!!!!!!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e8a6d54c-856f-4a7c-b2b0-c5dd495236fe/20240406_104602.jpg)

*   **_NXT WOMENS CHAMPIONSHIP LYRA VALKYRIA VS ROXANNE PEREZ_**
    

Roxanne worked Lyra Valkyria's arm for the entire match. Hilarious moment where Tatum Paxley tries to help Lyra and fails then gets kicked out. That’s your spot. Lol

*   **_WINNER AND NEW NXT WOMENS CHAMPION ROXANNE_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/22df22e4-5100-4a9c-bb83-7b7831c48615/20240406_110613.jpg)

*   **_NXT CHAMPIONSHIP ILJA DRAGUNOV VS TONY D'ANGELO_**
    

They worked over Ilja's hand for most of the match. Tony D'Angelo really showed out here. Stacks tried several times to interfere. H-BOMB THROUGH THE FRECKING TABLE MY GOODNESS. Phenomenal match.

*   **_WINNER AND STILL NXT CHAMPION ILJA DRAGUNOV_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bc5df07a-a036-45e9-8251-f28a83268d3d/20240406_110959.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/109c5c59-c24b-4e1d-9af8-a9a1ce064a16/20240406_114249.jpg)

*   **_CARMELO HAYES VS TRICK WILLIAMS_**
    

Top tier match full of heat and hatred. Tho it seemed to end right as it hit that 3rd gear.

*   **_WINNER: TRICK WILLIAMS_**
    

